================================================================================

This project uses components from the Python standard library,
licensed under the Python Software Foundation License (PSF License):
https://docs.python.org/3/license.html
https://docs.python.org/3/library/index.html

- __future__ — Future statement definitions

- gc — Garbage Collector interface for memory management
- inspect — Inspect live objects
- sys — System-specific parameters and functions
- os — Miscellaneous operating system interfaces for file and directory management
- tempfile — Generate temporary files and directories
- shutil - High-level file operations

- typing — Support for type hints (Any, TextIO)
- collections — Container datatypes
- collections.abc — Abstract Base Classes for Containers
- time — Time access and conversions
- datetime — Basic date and time types

- urllib — URL handling modules
- urllib.parse — Parse URLs into components

- csv — CSV File Reading and Writing
- json — JSON encoder and decoder
- sqlite3 — DB-API 2.0 interface for SQLite databases

- winsound — Sound-playing interface for Windows only

- unittest — Unit testing framework
- unittest.mock — mock object library

